OL,3,CLaurence Fox denies encouraging people
OL,4,Cto damage Ulez cameras
OL,6,FLaurence Fox has denied encouraging
OL,7,Fpeople to damage ultra low emission
OL,8,Fzone (Ulez) cameras in London.
OL,10,FThe actor-turned-politician is accused
OL,11,Fof posting messages on X between
OL,12,FSeptember 12 and October 4 2023 "which
OL,13,Fwere capable of encouraging the
OL,14,Fcommission of an either-way offence".
OL,16,FIn some of his posts Fox, 46,
OL,17,Fallegedly wrote about the cameras
OL,18,Fbeing torn down and praised anti-Ulez
OL,19,Factivists known as "Blade Runners",
OL,20,FWestminster Magistrates' Court heard
OL,21,Fon Friday.
