OL,3,CLaurence Fox denies encouraging people
OL,4,Cto damage Ulez cameras
OL,6,FHe appeared in court to plead not
OL,7,Fguilty to a charge of intentionally
OL,8,Fencouraging or assisting the
OL,9,Fcommission of an either-way offence.
OL,11,FTFL said that in the relevant period
OL,12,Fthere were some 700 incidents of
OL,13,Fdamage to cameras with a cost of more
OL,14,Fthan #920,000, prosecutors say.
