OL,3,CLaurence Fox denies encouraging people
OL,4,Cto damage Ulez cameras
OL,6,FVehicles that do not meet minimum
OL,7,Femissions standards are required to
OL,8,Fpay a #12.50 daily fee when used in
OL,9,Fthe Ulez zone, or face a fine.
OL,11,FVideos have been posted online showing
OL,12,F"Blade Runners" cutting the cameras'
OL,13,Fwires or completely removing the
OL,14,Fdevices.
